{"tid":2163792,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[炒哂車］Michelle Obama 話侵侵‘掟（非法入境）細路入籠’ 被左報FC 啲籠同政策係佢老公搞既","createTime":"2020-08-19T00:57:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T06:45:51.000Z","uid":48083,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"458e2c2bb9a892f003f1bc70a1247fe50cd04b6f","tid":2163792,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T00:57:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/tombevanrcp/status/1295683711061688322?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftombevanrcp%2Fstatus%2F1295683711061688322%3Fs%3D21&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5r9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=e23ea977\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftombevanrcp%2Fstatus%2F1295683711061688322%3Fs%3D21&h=43b39fe8\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/tombevanrcp/status/1295683711061688322?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\nWASHINGTON (AP) &mdash; Michelle Obama assailed President Donald Trump on Monday for ripping migrant children from their parents and throwing them into cages, picking up on a frequent and distorted point made widely by Democrats.<br />\n<br />\nShe's right that Trump's now-suspended policy at the U.S.-Mexico border separated thousands of children from their families in ways that had not been done before.<strong><span class=\"red\"> But what she did not say is that the very same &ldquo;cages&rdquo; were built and used in her husband's administration, for the same purpose of holding migrant kids temporarily.</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nMICHELLE OBAMA, on Americans: &ldquo;They watch in horror as children are torn from their families and thrown into cages.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nTHE FACTS: The reference to cages is misleading and a matter that Democrats have persistently distorted.<br />\n<br />\nTrump used facilities that were built during the Obama-Biden administration to house children at the border. They are chain-link enclosures inside border facilities where migrants were temporarily housed, separated by sex and age."},{"pid":"d95d825ba909c8ba688002548535956b86b2de09","tid":2163792,"uid":810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T00:59:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d5af8b4f79350b0651c8ba6fc1db4345e0b0e3e","tid":2163792,"uid":58630,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T01:01:49.000Z","msg":"黑人係咁 仲話blm 笑死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bb6499ff6b73982fdbaa72660d870c04531b6f2","tid":2163792,"uid":286897,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T01:04:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"65b4319f08de0d3a12775a1ed02c19296523537a","tid":2163792,"uid":269202,"like":8,"dislike":9,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T01:07:36.000Z","msg":"撐trump為道德？<br />\n<br />\n我覺得不少民運人士支持他，只係因為佢攻擊我既敵人<br />\n<br />\n奧也不見得真有道德，他對港立場是偏軟<br />\n奧巴馬表面受歡迎，但他在以聖經立國的美國卻放寬多項道德上事情。<br />\n<br />\n任內白人至上激化，為trump的白人至上群組提價了土壤和養分"},{"pid":"00f01b5657a920e7c940e8a68367b79b2ed9f267","tid":2163792,"uid":51828,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T01:11:44.000Z","msg":"你估佢唔知咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  之前hollywood班撚樣出黎屌侵果時己經比人問點解係obama時期冇出聲 個個靜哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da2af73d408969aad1d28e5dffb574acbdc304b2","tid":2163792,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T01:18:03.000Z","msg":"律政司介入西灣河開槍警案 Twitter<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2162970\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2162970</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"329adcdf6b2c8276e3495ca0f7846f555369aa00","tid":2163792,"uid":261937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"r